Hakusensha's Le Paradis (Rakuen) manga anthology magazine announced on Friday that KÃ´ji Kumeta (Sayonara, Zetsubou-Sensei, Joshiraku, The Eccentric Family character design) will draw a new manga in the magazine's next issue on February 28. The magazine describes the story as about a "Naked Prince" who is skillful at stripping down facades and true intentions all at once.

The preview does not specify if the new title will be a series or a one-shot.
